Figs 
<number box="[583,592,576,597]" pageId="5" pageNumber="98" value="1.0">1</number>
</figureCitation>
E, 
<number box="[621,630,576,597]" pageId="5" pageNumber="98" value="1.0">1</number>
F); face broad in both sexes (Oriental)............... 
