<keyLead pageId="5" pageNumber="98">
<number box="[151,163,723,744]" pageId="5" pageNumber="98" value="3.0">3</number>
Thorax densely grey pruinose, 
<number box="[521,533,723,744]" pageId="5" pageNumber="98" value="6.0">6</number>
dorsocentrals with fifth pair strongly offset medially; abdomen dark grey-brown to partly yellow; face broad in both sexes; male hind basitarsus with comma-shaped posterobasal projection; crossvein dm-cu located near middle of wing (
<number box="[385,398,782,803]" pageId="5" pageNumber="98" value="6.0">6</number>
